<br>
Sony = money grubbers who will hire people who may love the genre and who can get the game done, while there are other develepers who love the genre themselves, and who hire people who love it all as much as they do.<br>
<br>
If you ever played BG or BG2 you know what I mean, I hope.  There's TLC in it, you can feel it when you play.  It's like you are having fun with the game, and like a good book, you feel like the author is smiling over your shoulder as you enjoy it.  <br>
<br>
