Dead on. There WILL be a monumental MMORPG along the way here that combines that classic brilliance found in Baldur's Gate with the addicting online qualities of EQ. Will it be EQ2? Hard to say at this point, but doubtful. It won't be Shadowbane. Or AC2. Or AO2. WoW looks like it has the potential .. and knowing Blizzard it will rock. NWN will be a very interesting experiment .. and without a doubt SWG will be huge huge huge.<br>
